subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] Using Quickscript
msgSnippet: ... I don t believe I use any joins or alternate forms not listed in QM.  I have tried to avoid deviation so as to preserve the purity of my Quikscript
messageBody:
At 08:43 PM 12/1/2000 -0500, Jon wrote:
> Let me ask--do any of you personally use any joins or alternate forms
>besides those in QM or CFPB?

I don't believe I use any joins or alternate forms not listed in QM. I
have tried to avoid deviation so as to preserve the "purity" of my
Quikscript writing in isolation against the hope that someone else would
express some interest. And lo, my prayers were answered!

I join Gig at the top, bottom or both depending on the letter preceding and
following.

Paige.
